VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (?i)(apiKey|api_key|secret|privateKey|encryptionKey|password|token)\s*[:=]\s*["'][A-Za-z0-9/+]{16,}["']
WHEN EXPR MISSING:example|sample|dummy|test|placeholder|Keychain
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects likely hardcoded cryptographic keys or credentials in iOS Swift/Objective-C source.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for Hardcoded Cryptographic Key or Secret.
